{"parentUuid":"5ed7b33e-5af8-4439-9d8b-cb94347882df","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/home/adrien/Nextcloud/IdEst/Projets/MiscMetabar","sessionId":"7fcf0a8b-219a-4347-9d06-1f8d681db811","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"dev","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Build the pkgdown documentation website and the R package source tarball.\n\n## Steps\n\nRun the following commands **in sequence**, capturing all output:\n\n1. Rebuild README from `README.Rmd`:\n```r\nRscript -e \"devtools::build_readme()\"\n```\n\n2. Regenerate documentation:\n```r\nRscript -e \"devtools::document()\"\n```\n\n3. Rebuild the NEWS page:\n```r\nRscript -e \"pkgdown::build_news()\"\n```\n\n4. Build the full pkgdown site (lazy — only rebuilds changed pages):\n```r\nRscript -e \"devtools::build_site(lazy=TRUE)\"\n```\n\n5. Build the package source tarball:\n```r\nRscript -e \"devtools::build()\"\n```\n\n6. Lint the package (CodeFactor verification):\n```r\nRscript -e \"results <- lintr::lint_package(); print(results); cat('\\nTotal lint issues:', length(results), '\\n')\"\n```\n\n## After each step\n\n- Report success or summarise any errors/warnings.\n- If a step fails, explain the likely cause and propose a fix.\n\n## Important rules\n\n- **Never modify code, documentation, or any file without explicit user approval.**\n- Present each proposed fix with a before/after diff and ask \"Should I apply this fix?\" before making any change.\n"}]},"isMeta":true,"uuid":"38243146-d2f4-4006-8d3d-0128c1ab529f","timestamp":"2026-03-04T07:49:41.995Z","sourceToolUseID":"toolu_01Ko939CduXsuVEEAhmEZBUs"}
